MOTION DOCKET

90-2236. State v. D’Ambrosio.

Cuyahoga County, No. 57448. On motion for leave to file reply brief. Motion denied.

A.W. Sweeney, J., dissents.

On motion for leave to file supplemental brief. Motion denied.

A.W. Sweeney, J., dissents.

On motion to remove counsel. Motion denied.

Pfeifer, J., would also strike all pro se filings in this cause.
